Author: Regnar#6164
Content: I know it isn't a thing Komodo does often but I've been thinking about how to get a better grasp on a general "road map" of sorts within the ecosystem. For example, looking at CC-Assets(tokens) I see some cool proof of concepts being made (I worked on some admittedly less cool ones here). Or the current development on the gaming SDKs, etc. Any Idea on how to display progress on these different things to give someone a single directory to learn about all the different work being done?

Content: and by progress I don't mean commits, but more general terms that would be more "road map" like
